  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/applicationservices\/colorsync_manager\/1560541-parametric_types\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T13:51:51Z\n---\n\n# Parametric Types\n\nSpecify a parametric curve type enumeration,\n\n## Constants\n\n- **cmParametricType0**:  Y = X^gamma\n- **cmParametricType1**: Y = (aX+b)^gamma     [X>=-b\/a],  Y = 0    [X<-b\/a]\n- **cmParametricType2**: Y = (aX+b)^gamma + c [X>=-b\/a],  Y = c    [X<-b\/a]\n- **cmParametricType3**: Y = (aX+b)^gamma     [X>=d],     Y = cX   [X<d]\n- **cmParametricType4**: Y = (aX+b)^gamma + e [X>=d],     Y = cX+f [X<d]\n\n",
